60	\section{Mathlib gap}
61	
62	Mathlib has the constituent infrastructure for the \emph{definition} (Definition~\ref{def:Pic_functor}):
63	\begin{itemize}
64	  \item Fiber products of schemes.
65	  \item Line bundles and Picard groups (this project, Chapter~\ref{chap:Picard_LineBundle}).
66	  \item Pull-back of line bundles (this project, Chapter~\ref{chap:Picard_LineBundle}).
67	  \item Quotient groups for group quotients.
68	  \item Functor machinery for assembling the contravariant functor.
69	\end{itemize}
